Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您只派了幾個新人去追佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子的現狀也不容樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也採取了一些相應的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務已經決定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把事情處理完就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助離開了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有兩天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前去追趕的鳴人他們也沒有消息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連小李也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致情況我已經瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果鳴人和佐助有個三長兩短的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先四下分散追蹤鳴人和佐助的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人和佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個傢伙到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體情況稍後再做說明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先處理正事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認他們的氣味後通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會立刻趕過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾親眼目睹過他們的對決
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在讓她別擔心也不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停不下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別總是想著復仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便復仇成功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下的也只有空虛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在我面前擺出一副什麼都知道的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我都很不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是最不幸的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是都找到最重要的夥伴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為曾經失去才會瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以教你千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為你有了最重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是用來攻擊同伴或者復仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底該如何去運用它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太天真了 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可能真的會置對方於死地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要趕上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我就說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也正如你所願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在卡卡西和小櫻都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會像上次那樣被人阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我們一定要做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打到你求饒為止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算痛扁你一頓也要帶你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 你是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助當時用這種口氣對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想用螺旋丸來確認
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能和我全力發出的千鳥不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那招…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你究竟有多強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個拖後腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的極限是兩發 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是超過了兩發 又會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要發動第三發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你勉強發動忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非但無法順利使出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉還會歸零
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好會送命的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不能再做無謂的攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續剛才那樣的勢均力敵毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經完全確定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想置我於死地…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先用快招和忍術擾亂他的行動找到破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用千鳥作最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果同為一流的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要交手過一次 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能彼此看穿對方的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便嘴上不說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看穿我真正的心思了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁.鳳仙火之術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你總是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初我知道有人和我一樣後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得好安心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我一直想和你說話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 始終沒能開口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都在行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一直很受大家歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你我相差太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不甘心並視你為自己的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想輸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你越叫我拖後腿的 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越不想輸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使進入了第七班以後 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一切如舊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很固執 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有說出真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實我真的很想變得和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我…憧憬的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和你分個高下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時 我真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是你第一次認同我所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我即便不用交手也能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時開始 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然嘴上沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們…是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻真的想置我於死地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在連你剛才說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真是假都分不清
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許只有我一廂情願地…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正當你是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今已經晚了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太沒面子了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不明白這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…被大蛇丸帶走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然用左手擋住了我對心臟的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在已經沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經使不出剛才的招式了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股不斷湧出的紅色查克拉
